Question: What will we be able to do creating images with Pango?
 We will be able to create art in many different styles and variations.

How will this help us create, more better art?
 This will help us create better art by giving much more different tools to
 use than what we are comfortable with.

Do you remember the for loop? How might we use that with Pango to make art?
 we might use for loops to make many pictures at the same time making our
 lives easier and giving us many outcomes to pick from.
